The paper deals with image coding using deep learning techniques, which suggests that it could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories. The most likely category is cs.MM (Multimedia), which deals with multimedia content analysis, processing, and retrieval. The paper also involves computer vision techniques, which makes cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) another likely category. The paper also involves information theory and compression techniques, which suggests that it could belong to cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also involves deep learning techniques, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
